org.apache.flink.runtime.instance

Class SimpleSlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.instance.Slot
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.instance.SimpleSlot

  • public class SimpleSlot
extends Slot
    Class which represents a single slot on a machine or within a shared slot. If this slot is part of a [[SharedSlot]], then its parent attribute is set to this instance. If not, then the parent attribute is null. IMPORTANT: This class has no synchronization. Thus it has to be synchronized by the calling object.
